title: File:Plaque in Fairbanks Alaska.jpg
author: RadioKAOS
description: Plaque in Golden Heart Plaza in downtown Fairbanks, Alaska. This plaque was installed in the 1980s with the names of Fairbanks residents. This photo was uploaded here primarily to illustrate a point made in the book Mr. Whitekeys' Alaska Bizarre, which contains a section on Fairbanks and points out that a man named "Dick Flopalotofit" is next to a man named "Stubby" on the plaque.
